At last!
Finally I've finnished my work experiance!(king's mill)
Making about 100 cups of tea being the nurses skivvy really is enough for one day never mind two whole weeks!i havent really done a lot apart from that.but whatwas i expecting to do!?oh i dont know, but...not that.And hanging around with old people isnt all that bad, made some good friends:D.
But just to start my last day on the right note, just walking in the main entrance a man attatched to a drip with numerous tattoos and a wacky grey hair doo, pajama's and slippers on says 'alrate love, got a fag?'..well i didn't, but even if i did he wouldnt have got one..though i did see him later same place but with a fag this time.
But anyway..yeah just glad i dont have to go back any time soon.i hope.!
